Want to know where is your parcel? It’s easy! Just use all-in-one “Parcel Track” app to easily track all your parcels, shipments, online orders from 1000+ parcel delivery services around the world, such as: UPS, USPS, Amazon, DHL, FedEx, DPD, GLS, EMS, TNT, Yodel, Australia Post, PostNord, Hermes, Aquiline, Bpost, DTDC, DSV, Asendia, Aramex and others. Full list of supported carriers is available in the app.

Now there is no need to install many apps from different parcel delivery services, such as: UPS mobile, USPS mobile, FedEx and others to track your parcels. Save your device storage and allow all-in-one “Parcel Track” app to make this job for all of them.

“Parcel Track” App Main Features:
- Fast and convenient tracking of all your parcels, shipments, online orders by tracking number;
- 1000+ parcel delivery services around the world available for tracking;
- Barcode Scanner - allows you to quickly add your parcel tracking number to track and not to enter it manually;
- Full Parcel Tracking History - shows you all parcel movement history and actual delivery status, also displays parcel route on the map;
- Convenient search and management - allows you to quickly find the parcel, as well as deleting parcels that you don’t need anymore;
- Home Screen Widgets - show you current tracking information about your recently added parcels;
- No ads!

“Parcel Track” app is useful for businesses that need to track many parcels at the same time, as well as for online shopping lovers. It all depends on your needs.

How to add widget to your Home Screen?
1. From the Home Screen, touch and hold a widget or an empty area until the apps jiggle.
2. Tap the “+” Add button in the upper-left corner.
3. Search for “Parcel” and select the Parcel Track app from the list.
4. Select a widget, choose a widget size, then tap Add Widget.
5. Tap Done.

Please note that free version of the app is limited to:
– 1 Parcel Tracking;
If you want to use the app without limits an auto-renewable subscriptions ”Parcel Track Pro” are available.

Auto-renewable Subscriptions ”Parcel Track Pro” Info:
By subscribing you get premium (full, unlimited) access to all the features and content offered by ”Parcel Track” app.

Auto-renewable Subscriptions ”Parcel Track Pro” Includes:
– Tracking in 1000+ Carriers;
– Track Parcels Unlimited;
– Full Tracking History With Map;
– Home Screen Widgets;

The app contains the following auto-renewable subscriptions called ”Parcel Track Pro”:
– Weekly (2,99 US$) with a 3-days for free period;
– Monthly (9,99 US$);
– Yearly (29,99 US$);
